CREATE TABLE [dbo].[config]
( 
	[Category] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[TABLE_SCHEMA] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[TABLE_NAME] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[COLUMN_NAME] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Data_Type] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Data_Length] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[PII_Level] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Pattern_Type] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Pattern] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Parameter_CONFIG] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[Lookup] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[SOURCE_OF_CONFIG] [varchar](300)  NULL,
	[CYCLE_ID] [varchar](300)  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
